{
  "stem": "10353.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I managed to get to the edge of the-- of the-- of my row.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And as we were marching, marching, marching-- and they were going around with the-- with their rifles, you know, and their bayonets against us to see that nobody gets out of line.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But as we came to one intersection, I managed to tear away and to separate and I started running.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So where do I run now?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they said that there is one company, such a brigade that was left in Budapest for the purpose to clean up after the air raids.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they're primary composed of people from my home town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I got myself in after some lengthy going and walking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I got in there and-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I got in there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I asked them that they should take me into the company.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they couldn't do it officially.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So after a couple of days, in the meantime, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was hiding out in a cellar during the night and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] tried to work that I should be taken into this company.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So finally after two days, I understand that they bribed one of the officers and they took me in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as I was ready to go in to the quarters of this compound, I saw three-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] three huge trucks came in and gendarmes and Arrow Cross guys were surrounding this company.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I took off right away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't go into the quarters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I start running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But where do you run?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I remember getting onto the street car.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
